Introduction

Xdinary Heroes is a boy band under Studio J and JYP Entertainment. Their name is an abbreviation of "Extra Ordinary Heroes", meaning "anyone can become a hero". They made their official debut on December 6, 2021, with the digital single "Happy Death Day".

On February 29, 2024, it was announced that Xdinary Heroes would release a soundtrack, their first ever, for the webtoon Killer Pedro titled "Wego Wego" on March 8th.

On April 12, 2024, the group released a mood film for their first full-length album Troubleshooting, released on April 30.
